                <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/6069530/pexels-photo-6069530.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&h=650&w=940" alt="Cardigan" class="rounded-3 object-fit-cover" style="width: 100%; height: 100%;">
